
'''= "What does the Land Society CIC do?We provide support for affordable community self build housing". (UK)'''

URL = http://www.landsociety.org/


=Description=

"We support people in housing need in towns and villages to self build their own affordable home. We provide all the technical and professional input to enable people to get together as a community in a Community Land Trust (CLT) to buy suitable land and build energy efficient, affordable, sustainable homes.

At the moment we are mainly working in Teignbridge and Torbay in South Devon. Over the next two or three years we expect to also start working in adjacent areas in the South West of England."


